phrases: Episode 13 We Picked Up Something Crazy!
Next on Morioh Radio, we have a letter from Troubled Lonesome Boy.
I cannot get a hold of my girlfriend at all and it is making me blue.
I wonder if she is mad because I proposed suddenly.
And I spent all my pay on an engagement ring with a ruby, her birthstone...
So you were able to successfully retrieve the bow and arrow.
He would been committing burglaries with his Stand.
The police are still looking into it.
Try doing something with your Stand again.
I will send you to the ends of the Earth and kill you there.
I will be safest in prison!
Even if he gets out of jail, I am sure he will not try anything again.
Jotaro, what are you going to do with the bow and arrow?
The Speedwagon Foundation is going to hold on to it and research it.

That means this incident's been resolved!
It did not end up being that big a deal, but yay!
I am still questioning Otoishi about the Stand

Coffee in Japan is still the best.

I look away for a second and...
Josuke, do not you have to go?
The bus will be here soon.
I wonder if those two will be okay.
Whoa, this cake is so good!
Can I get another slice, waitress?
Hello, this is the Higashikata resid
It is unusual for you to call me.
Hey, y-you are going to be home all day today, right?
As long as you are there, it is fine.
He would better not be planning something weird again.
I hope Mom did not think that was weird.

Did you just call for me?

so we are going to take the bus to my house.

You can only look from a distance.

She is going to be a wreck.
I am going to be calling you Mr. Joestar.
I might as well lay it on the line now.
I mean, it might seem cold,
but calling someone I just met Dad or Pops is just not happening.
So after you see my mom, I want you to go right back to America.
I know it is best to be honest, but still,
there are some things between people that just are not possible.
Excuse me, did you see where the burly old man who was just here went?
He got onto that long-distance bus.
You said we were getting on a bus, so...
But I am surprised you caught up to the bus by running.
We were just about to get onto the freeway.
Right now, I am thinking it might have been better to just let you go...
Something seems to be pulling on my trousers.
Do not let them drag you off somewhere again.
There is a Stand user nearby!
Anyway, is there a vending machine nearby?
There is no way I am letting him see my mom.
Now he is seeing and hearing things.
This old man is seriously bad news.
Get out of here, you mutt!

I can tell when I am touching it.

But how did a baby turn invisible out here?
I am assuming it is a Stand ability, but...
There are a lot of questions, like, Why did the enemy
Stand user make it invisible, and Where is its mom?
Josuke, I think the baby is actually the Stand user.
It is a Stand user without realizing it.
Because it is been separated from its mother, it instinctively went invisible.
Even adults can develop ulcers, spot baldness, and gray hair
before they realize it for psychological reasons, right?
I believe that finding its mother will be the way to solve this.
H-Hey, just hurry up and make it stop crying.
I-I am not really sure what to do, either.
I did something similar to this, but that was a very long time ago.
Yes, when I just touched it now.
Right, the way to tell if it is a boy or a girl is between the legs!
Did you find out something else?
I-Is there one on your hand?
I-It is invisible, so I could not tell for sure until I could smell it.
And I just scratched my beard with this hand!
I am returning your manuscript to you.
I will be looking forward to those fixes for the volumes, Sensei.
For the time being, we are going to have to get milk and diapers.
And since she is naked, we need to get her some clothes.
I am counting on you, Mr. Joestar.
It would be too embarrassing for me to buy baby goods.
a 16-year-old delinquent like me got some girl pregnant.

You can use my credit card.
Do not buy anything too expensive.
I have worked hard to build up my savings, and I do not have much!
Can I help you find something?
Is this your first time here?
These diapers are easy to change, even if you are living on your own.
You will not have to worry overnight, either.
I am looking for a baby, not myself.
So you are looking for baby diapers.
Were you looking for cloth diapers, or disposable pull-ups?
As you can see, this one will need a diaper cover,
but the disposable pull-up is simple and economical.
I-I do not really know, so could you just...
we have newborn, S-size, M-size, L-size, XL-size, boys' and girls'.
Th-There are that many options nowadays?
W-Well, she is a girl, and when I held her, she was about this big.
What do you mean by when I held her, sir?
It would be inconvenient for us if you bought diapers
that were too big, and then
tried to return them after they have been pooped in.
Give me all of the sizes.
I also need baby wipes, powdered milk, and baby bottles...
For baby bottles, we have glass or plastic.
Glass ones do not scratch or start to smell as easily,
but they are a bit heavy for a baby to hold.
The plastic ones are light, but may have a noticeable smell.
We also have various shapes and designs.
We have ones shaped like rocket ships and racing cars.
This one, the baby can hold by itself.
And this one, if you turn it upside-down, the doll inside moves.
I-I have no idea, so if you could just throw in a few...
And which bottle nipples would you like, sir?
Rubber ones are soft, but do not last very long.
Silicon ones last, but are a bit hard.
This one is called a Chupatoreni.
There is a diaphragm where the nipple goes in the mouth,
and the flow of milk is adjusted by how hard the baby sucks on it.
This is a NUK from Germany.
The shape is slightly flattened, and is said to
more closely resemble a mother's natural shape.
And just like when drinking breast milk, it will not come out
Just give me all of them.
As for the nipple holes, we have round, Y-shaped, and cross-shaped varieties.
J-Just give me all of them.
And some baby clothes and socks, too.
I will be paying by card.
130,000... I do not really understand yen that well.
I wonder how much that is in dollars.
I did not waste any money, and it is just baby stuff.
I am sure it cannot be that expensive.
The girl who got the ring.
I wonder what happened with that.
Since he did not get an answer, I wonder if that was a no.
They could be super conflicted about it.
If people from school find me here...
Sorry to keep you waiting, Josuke.
Now we will not have to worry about losing sight of her, but...
If strangers see that she does not have a face, they will be creeped out.
Let us try some foundation first.
Hey, I think she might actually be cute.
This face will help us find her mom.
We have finally got some hope.
All right, now let us try some lipstick.
And let us draw on some eyebrows and eyelashes...
I knew he would do that...
So this geezer's the type to get carried away when you compliment him.
Now we can finally take you around without having to worry too much.
We cannot put makeup on your eyes, so we will just have to use sunglasses.
Maybe I went too light on the foundation.
It looks like it is starting to come off...
This baby's not just making herself invisible!
She is making everything around her invisible, too!
I am telling you to hurry up and let go of the baby!

It looks like everything within about thirty centimeters
of that baby is becoming invisible.
But this does not make sense.
If she keeps trying to protect herself with her Stand,
who could even feed her or take care of her?
So it must be due to feelings of anxiety.
She does not want to be touched by someone she does not know.
If she powers up any more, no one will be able to get near her.
We will end up invisible, too.
I wonder who is going to clean it up.
Well, I guess someone will do it.
What the hell are you doing, Mr. Joestar?!
Do not space out at a time like this!
The more scared she gets, the wider her range gets!
That is the sound of the stroller flipping over!
The invisible baby... fell into the water?!
I cannot even see any bubbles!
This all happened because he could not keep it together.
This irresponsible guy is my father?
He is so irresponsible, he was okay with abandoning my mom for sixteen years.
There is no way in hell I can respect someone like him.
There is no way we can get along.
She should be right around here.
I do not care if I turn invisible, too.
Just hurry up and touch me!
How the hell am I supposed to find
an invisible baby in clear water?!
might die in just a moment, so when that happens,
please give my regards to your mother.
What the hell are you doing?!
I am adding color to the water...
The color of the blood is turning more and more invisible.
The child is in the center.
No one else would think to do this.
Not for someone else's child, who they have never seen before...
They would not go this far.
But it looks like everything worked out for now.
O-One hundred and thirty thousand yen?!
The savings I worked so hard for...
